                    <div class="accordion-item mb-3"
                        style="border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                        <h3 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#faq10" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq10"
                                style="background-color: var(--color-bg-light); border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px;">
                                <strong>Is my library data secure?</strong>
                            </button>
                        </h3>
                        <div id="faq10" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body" style="padding: 20px;">
                                Absolutely! Security is our top priority. We host MyLibrarian on Microsoft's Azure
                                platform,
                                which provides enterprise-level security with industry-leading compliance certifications
                                including SOC 2 Type II, ISO 27001, and GDPR compliance. Your data is protected with
                                enterprise-grade encryption both in transit and at rest, and we maintain regular
                                automated
                                backups with point-in-time recovery capabilities. Microsoft's global infrastructure
                                ensures
                                99.9% uptime and world-class security monitoring. Your library data is never shared with
                                third parties and you maintain full ownership of your content.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ Item 11 -->
                    <div class="accordion-item mb-3"
